body: Also, see [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/4807#issuecomment-256718844) for perf impact. The importance of fast IDCT varies by image size, and of course its impact on training depends on how compute-heavy the model is (less impact for Inception, more for AlexNet).
